  <zone type="main">
    <line>[f. 36r is blank]</line>
    <line rend="indent1">The storm of sound is driven <unclear reason="illegible"
      >a</unclear>long</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Sucked up &amp; hurrying&#8212;as they fleet</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Behind its gathering billows meet</line>
    <line rend="indent1">And to the fatal mountain bear</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Like clouds amid the yielding air</line>
    <line rend="left"><add><metamark function="count">264</metamark></add></line>
    <line><add><metamark function="displacement" xml:id="e2-0074.03">&#60;</metamark></add></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:scene" spanTo="#e2-0074.01"/>
    <line rend="center">Scene 3. A pinnacle of rock among</line>
    <line>Mountains &#8212; <add>Asia &amp; Panthea</add></line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0074.01"/>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0074.02"/>
    <line rend="center">Panthea</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0074.02"/>
    <line>Hither the sound has borne us&#8212; <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten"><unclear reason="illegible">'tis</unclear></del>
        <add place="intralinear">to</add>
      </mod> the realm</line>
    <line>Of Demogorgon, &amp; the mighty portal</line>
    <line>Like a Volcano's meteor-breathing chasm</line>
    <line>Whence the oracular vapour is breathed up</line>
    <line>Which lonely men drink wandering in their youth</line>
    <line>And call truth, virtue, love, genius or joy</line>
    <line>That maddening wine of life, whose dregs they drain</line>
    <line>To deep intoxication, &amp; uplift</line>
    <line>Like Maenads who cry loud Evoe! Evoe!</line>
    <line>The voice which is contagion to the world.</line>
  </zone>
